---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="AI Integration & Automation | Intelio - Connect, Automate, Optimize" description="Make your existing systems intelligent. Connect CRMs, accounting, operations, and data systems. Automate workflows and embed AI into operations.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- SECTION 1: HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-slate-900 to-gray-900">
    <!-- Video Background -->
    <video 
      autoplay 
      loop 
      muted 
      playsinline
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
    >
      <source src="/logos/Cinematic_Finance_Animation_Generation (1).mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    
    <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900/95 via-gray-900/80 to-gray-900/60 z-[1]"></div>
    
    <!-- Subtle noise texture -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] mix-blend-overlay z-[2]" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\'100\' height=\'100\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%3E%3Cfilter id=\'noise\'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=\'fractalNoise\' baseFrequency=\'0.9\' numOctaves=\'4\'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=\'100%25\' height=\'100%25\' filter=\'url(%23noise)\'/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Label -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
            AI INTEGRATION & AUTOMATION
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
          AI Integration & Automation
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subhead -->
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Make your existing systems intelligent. Connect, automate, optimize.
        </p>
        
        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-black hover:bg-gray-800 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          Start a Project
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: INTRO -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-8">
        Your Systems Should Work Together
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Most businesses run on disconnected tools, manual handoffs, and workflows held together by spreadsheets and institutional knowledge.
        </p>
        <p>
          AI Integration & Automation connects your existing systems, automates repetitive work, and embeds intelligence directly into operations.
        </p>
        <p>
          This goes far beyond simple integrations—covering system design, automation architecture, and AI applied where it removes friction or scales decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-black">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          You keep the tools that work. We make them work better—together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: WHAT WE BUILD -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black mb-4 block">WHAT WE BUILD</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1: System Integration -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">System Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Connect CRMs, accounting, operations, and data systems. One connected stack.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>CRM ↔ accounting ↔ operations sync</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>ERP and database integrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Cross-platform data pipelines</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ai-integration-automation/system-integration" class="text-black font-semibold hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Workflow Automation -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Workflow Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Automate repetitive processes, approvals, handoffs, and data entry.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Lead routing and follow-up sequences</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Approval workflows and notifications</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Document generation and delivery</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ai-integration-automation/workflow-automation" class="text-black font-semibold hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: AI-Enhanced Operations -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">AI-Enhanced Operations</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Embed AI into existing workflows—document processing, intelligent routing, decision support.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Document extraction and classification</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Intelligent lead scoring</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Predictive alerts and recommendations</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ai-integration-automation/ai-enhanced-operations" class="text-black font-semibold hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Data Connectivity & Visibility -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Connectivity & Visibility</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Unified dashboards, real-time reporting, and data pipelines.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Executive dashboards across systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Real-time KPI tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-black mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Cross-department reporting</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ai-integration-automation/data-connectivity" class="text-black font-semibold hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: ENGAGEMENT MODELS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black mb-4 block">ENGAGEMENT MODELS</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1: Build + Maintain -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Build + Maintain</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">You run it. We keep it working.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We build and integrate intelligent systems, then maintain them as your business evolves.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Teams that want ownership without technical burden</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Structure</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Project fee + monthly maintenance</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Timeline</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">4–8 weeks initial build, then ongoing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Build + Operate -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Build + Operate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">We build and run it for you.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We build the system and operate it with or for you. Execution off your plate.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Lean teams, founders, ops-heavy businesses</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Structure</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Monthly operating retainer</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Timeline</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Ongoing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Managed Automation -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Managed Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">Continuous automation as a service</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Ongoing automation, AI integration, and optimization delivered as a managed service.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Mature operations, enterprise teams</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Structure</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Monthly subscription</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Timeline</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Ongoing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: OUR PROCESS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black mb-4 block">OUR PROCESS</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 01 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            01
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Map the Current State</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We start by understanding how your business actually operates—the tools, workflows, and where things break down.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 02 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            02
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Design the Connected System</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We architect the integrations, automations, and AI enhancements that eliminate friction.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 03 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            03
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Build & Integrate</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We build the automations, connect the systems, and integrate AI into your existing stack.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 04 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            04
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Operate or Hand Off</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We can train your team, maintain the system, or operate the entire thing for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 6: WHAT YOU GET -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12">
        What You Get
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Connected Systems</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Tools working together</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Automated Workflows</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Manual work removed</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">AI Where It Matters</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Intelligence embedded</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Real-Time Visibility</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Dashboards that show reality</p>
